<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/uk-sport> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "UK Sport (UKSP) supports Britain’s best Olympic and Paralympic sports and athletes, co-ordinating the bids for and staging of major international sporting events in the UK. It invests around £100 million each year in high performance sport. UKSP is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Culture, Media and Sport , supported by 1 public body ."@en .
